Revision history for Speech-Synthesis

0.01    August 8, 2005
        First version, support for SAPI4, SAPI5, MSAgent and MacSpeech
0.02    August 11, 2005
        Second release, supporting Festival too
0.03    August 12, 2005
        Fix in Festival support to get more information on installed voices
        Update in InstalledLanguages for Festival.
        Added host and port parameters to all methods so you could run
        your festival server on something else than localhost port 1319
